      "rationale": "The CFD solver (ANSYS Fluent 2023 R2) is operated under an ISO 9001-certified quality management system. Version control, regression test suite (>1200 test cases), and change management procedures are documented. Solver release notes and known-issue tracking confirm no open defects affecting hemolysis-relevant physics. Achieved level 4 meets required level 4 for MRL 5."
