      "rationale": "Method of manufactured solutions (MMS) applied to the incompressible Navier-Stokes solver and the power-law hemolysis transport equation. Observed order of accuracy (2.01 ± 0.04) matches theoretical second-order spatial discretization. Code verification suite results archived and traceable to solver release 2023 R2."
