      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study performed per Celik et al. (2008) GCI methodology. Fine-mesh GCI for NIH < 3.2%; apparent order p = 1.97. Temporal discretization error assessed via halved time-step study; hemolysis QoI change < 0.8%. Combined space-time discretization error budget included in Monte Carlo UQ propagation. Achieved level 4 meets required level 4."
