      "acceptanceCriteria": "https://uofa.net/synth/criteria/test-conditions-mrl5-criteria",
      "rationale": "In vitro test conditions (hematocrit 35%, temperature 37 ± 0.5 °C, anticoagulant protocol per ASTM F1841) are documented in the experimental protocol and confirmed traceable to the validation dataset. Flow rates and rotational speeds match the 5 COU operating points within ±1.2%. Achieved level 4 meets required level 4."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Output comparison",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
